data.description: Welcome home to this remodeled 3/2 townhome nestled in a peaceful community. This home offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and classic charm. A stylish townhome complete with both upgrades and appeal. Upgrades include a brand new roof that is scheduled for the next 2 months, remodeled bathrooms, kitchen & flooring. Kitchen features modern LG appliances. Between the new roof and accordion hurricane shutters you will sleep sound knowing you are safe & secure. A unique feature of this townhouse is that the master bedroom is on the ground floor with large walk in closet and that all the bedrooms are large & spacious, something that's hard to find in a townhouse. Step outside to an extremely large screened porch & tropical oasis perfect for entertaining. Priced to sell fast.
